title: Guizhou section of Tongren-Huaihua highway completed
content: Aerial photo taken on May 22, 2019 shows the Jinjiang grand bridge on the Tongren-Huaihua highway in southwest China's Guizhou Province. The construction of 33.778-kilometer-long Guizhou section of Tongren-Huaihua highway was completed on Tuesday. (Xinhua/Tao Liang)
